OL,3,CPolice investigate pub disorder
OL,4,Cinvolving 300 football fans after win
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for witnesses
OL,7,Fafter 300 football fans descended on a
OL,8,Fpub causing disorder including theft,
OL,9,Fcriminal damage and racial abuse after
OL,10,FPortsmouth FC's victory which secured
OL,11,Fthe team's place in the Championship.
OL,13,FThe incident at the O'Neill's pub in
OL,14,FAlbert Road, Southsea, happened after
OL,15,Fthe Hampshire club beat Barnsley 3-2
OL,16,Fat home on Tuesday evening to take the
OL,17,FLeague One title.
