OL,6,FA Hampshire police spokesman said: "It
OL,7,Fis believed around 300 people were
OL,8,Fpresent at the time, and we have
OL,9,Freceived reports of a number of
OL,10,Foffences, including theft, criminal
OL,11,Fdamage and racial abuse aimed at a
OL,12,Fstaff member.
OL,14,F"The disorder is reported to have
OL,15,Fcontinued into surrounding streets,
OL,16,Fwith people present then moving off in
OL,17,Freduced groups to other establishments
OL,18,Fas well.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
