OL,6,F"We have also received a report of
OL,7,Fcriminal damage in Drift Bar, and of a
OL,8,Fman being assaulted in Palmerston Road.
OL,10,F"Officers attended and remained in the
OL,11,Farea into the early hours of the
OL,12,Fmorning.
OL,14,F"Our enquiries continue, with officers
OL,15,Fpresent taking statements, seizing
OL,16,Fevidence and any CCTV footage, and
OL,17,Fidentifying all offences committed
OL,18,Fduring the disorder."
