OL,6,FChief Inspector Paul Markham said:
OL,7,F"Portsmouth's win against Barnsley was
OL,8,Fa fantastic moment for the club and
OL,9,Ffor the city, and a moment everyone
OL,10,Frightly wanted to celebrate.
OL,12,F"Sadly, a small number of people saw
OL,13,Fthis as an opportunity to commit
OL,14,Fmindless acts of violence and criminal
OL,15,Fdamage as part of the wider
OL,16,Fcelebrations.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
