OL,4,Cinvolving 300 football fans after win
OL,6,F"Officers have been out in Southsea
OL,7,Fand we are working hard to identify
OL,8,Fany and all offences committed and
OL,9,Fensure all lines of enquiry available
OL,10,Fare thoroughly investigated to
OL,11,Fidentify people responsible.
OL,13,F"If you do have any concerns or
OL,14,Finformation which may assist, then
OL,15,Fplease do not hesitate to speak with
OL,16,Fofficers or contact us with this.
