OL,6,F"The vast majority of those attending
OL,7,Fthe game were there to enjoy the
OL,8,Foccasion and wanted no involvement in
OL,9,Fany disorder, and we know this has
OL,10,Fbeen the case throughout the season.
OL,12,F"We will not tolerate the minority who
OL,13,Fwish to use events such as this one to
OL,14,Fcommit crime.
