OL,6,F"On Saturday, there will be football
OL,7,Fin Portsmouth again, with the final
OL,8,Fhome game of the season against Wigan.
OL,9,FWe consistently review our plans for
OL,10,Fall matchdays, and Tuesday night's
OL,11,Factions will form part of this review
OL,12,Fof our resources for the game."
